  m_Name: 3 jarix
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  planet: 3
  descriptions:
  - 'Jarix is a technologically advanced planet ruled by one of the largest intergalactic
    spacefuel corporations - Spacevoyage. '
  - 'Although the riches of this planet are immense, they are mostly held in the
    accounts of Spacevoyage executives. Due to this the planet is very diverse with
    various species inhabiting it. '
  - 'These factors result in Jarix having some of the worst life quality in the known
    universe. The centuries of industrial pollution have also made it quite a dark
    and dystopian looking place. '
  - Due to its technology, Jarixians were some of the first planets to join the Intergalactic
    championship so they have a long history of the sport being played despite a
    lack of natural talent.
